item.title: Fires
item.description: Akeneo PIM Community Standard Edition Welcome to Akeneo PIM Product. This repository is used to create a new PIM project based on Akeneo PIM. If you want to contribute to the Akeneo PIM (and we will be pleased if you do!), you can fork the repository https://github.com/akeneo/pim-community-dev and submit a pull request. Scrutinizer Crowdin Application Technical Information The following documentation is designed for both clients and partners and provides all technical information required to define required server(s) to run Akeneo PIM application and check that end users workstation is compatible with Akeneo PIM application: https://docs.
